pd.read_json("./Data/project/US_category_id.json")
import json
with open("./Data/project/US_category_id.json") as f:
    categories = json.load(f)["items"]
cat_dict = {}
for cat in categories:
    cat_dict[int(cat["id"])] = cat["snippet"]["title"]
df['category_name'] = df['category_id'].map(cat_dict)

from wordcloud import WordCloud, STOPWORDS
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
In [9]:
plt.figure(figsize = (100,100))

stopwords = set(STOPWORDS)

wordcloud = WordCloud(
                      background_color = 'white',
                      stopwords = stopwords,
                      max_words = 400,
                      width = 1200,
                      height = 600,
                      colormap = "tab20c"
                    ).generate(tags_word)

plt.imshow(wordcloud)
plt.title('WORD CLOUD for Tags', fontsize = 20)
plt.axis('off')
plt.show()

In [10]:
title_word = df['title'].str.lower().str.cat(sep=' ')
title_word = re.sub('[^A-Za-z]+', ' ', title_word)

plt.figure(figsize = (100,100))

stopwords = set(STOPWORDS)

wordcloud = WordCloud(
                      background_color = 'white',
                      stopwords = stopwords,
                      max_words = 400,
                      width = 1200,
                      height = 600,
                      colormap = "tab20b"
                    ).generate(title_word)

plt.imshow(wordcloud)
plt.title('WORD CLOUD for title', fontsize = 20)
plt.axis('off')
plt.show()
